    "One of the critical limitations of our research is the availability of high-quality and diverse medical image data of KUB X-rays of kidney stones.",
    "The quality and diversity of the dataset are crucial in identifying kidney stones.",
    "In the future, overcoming this limitation will require continued efforts to collect, curate, and make a broader range of medical image data more readily available to improve model performance.",
    "Even using XAI techniques such as LRP, the model's interpretation may still be inconspicuous or might not give meaningful insight into the model's decision-making.",
